OL,3,CCovid-19 inquiry chairwoman accused of
OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,FThe chairwoman of the Covid-19 inquiry
OL,7,Fhas been accused of a "U-turn" over
OL,8,Fthe probe's examination of how the
OL,9,Fpandemic affected mental health.
OL,11,FCharities including Mind and Rethink
OL,12,FMental Illness have joined forces with
OL,13,Fthe Centre for Mental Health, the
OL,14,FAssociation of Mental Health Providers
OL,15,Fand other groups to urge Baroness
OL,16,FHallett to think again about how the
OL,17,Fissue will be dealt with by the
OL,18,Finquiry.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@^O]
