OL,3,CCovid-19 inquiry chairwoman accused of
OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,FThey say the lack of focus on mental
OL,7,Fhealth "risks failing" millions of
OL,8,Fpeople with pre-existing illness,
OL,9,Falongside those who sought help during
OL,10,Fthe pandemic but were "turned away".
OL,12,FTerms of reference for the inquiry
OL,13,Fsaid it would look at "the impact on
OL,14,Fthe mental health and wellbeing of the
OL,15,Fpopulation, including but not limited
OL,16,Fto those who were harmed significantly
OL,17,Fby the pandemic" and "the impact on
OL,18,Fthe mental health and wellbeing of the
OL,19,Fbereaved".
