OL,3,CCovid-19 inquiry chairwoman accused of
OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,FMind submitted to Baroness Hallett
OL,7,Fthat Module 3 "should consider the
OL,8,Fimpact of the pandemic on wider mental
OL,9,Fhealth services" and not just look at
OL,10,Finpatient psychiatric care for
OL,11,Fchildren, as has been planned.
OL,13,FBaroness Hallett said she would "give
OL,14,Fthis submission further
OL,15,Fconsideration", including which area
OL,16,For module of the inquiry's work "is
OL,17,Fbest placed to examine these matters".
