OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,FHowever, she has since ruled that
OL,7,F"Module 3 cannot include the issue of
OL,8,Fthe impact of the pandemic on adult
OL,9,Fmental health services within its
OL,10,Fbroad provisional outline of scope and
OL,11,Fthe hearing time available".
OL,13,FShe said she will ensure the impact on
OL,14,Fmental health is covered by other
OL,15,Fmodules and through the inquiry's
OL,16,Fwider listening exercise.
