OL,3,CCovid-19 inquiry chairwoman accused of
OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,FIn an open letter calling for Baroness
OL,7,FHallett and inquiry staff to think
OL,8,Fagain, the charities and groups said:
OL,9,F"The Covid-19 Inquiry's refusal to
OL,10,Fexamine the mental health consequences
OL,11,Fof the pandemic risks failing the
OL,12,Fpeople with pre-existing mental health
OL,13,Fconditions who died at five times the
OL,14,Frate of the general population.
OL,16,F"It risks failing the eight million
OL,17,Fpeople who sought help with their
OL,18,Fmental health and were turned away.
OL,26,@qD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/14
