OL,3,CCovid-19 inquiry chairwoman accused of
OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,F"And it risks failing future
OL,7,Fgenerations by not allowing a proper
OL,8,Fexamination of what can be done better
OL,9,Fin the event of another pandemic."
OL,11,FThe letter, shared exclusively with
OL,12,Fthe PA news agency, has also been
OL,13,Fsigned by the British Psychological
OL,14,FSociety, Federation of Ethnic Minority
OL,15,FHealthcare Organisations, Family
OL,16,FAction, the Race Equality Foundation,
OL,17,FGroup B Strep Support, the Lullaby
OL,18,FTrust, the Miscarriage Association,
OL,19,FTommy's and the Association of Mental
OL,20,FHealth Providers Leads Network.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@bO]
