OL,3,CCovid-19 inquiry chairwoman accused of
OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,FThe letter went on: "Despite positive
OL,7,Findications from the last Module 3
OL,8,Fhearing that mental health would now
OL,9,Fbe fully considered by the inquiry, we
OL,10,Fare deeply disappointed by this U-turn.
OL,12,F"The exceptionally narrow focus on the
OL,13,Ffew inpatient beds that are provided
OL,14,Fto children and young people means
OL,15,Fserious questions will not be answered.
OL,26,@nD@UOUtD@AOU
