OL,3,CCovid-19 inquiry chairwoman accused of
OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,F"These questions include: Why was
OL,7,Fthere no public mental health plan?
OL,8,FWhy did those with pre-existing mental
OL,9,Fhealth conditions die at five times
OL,10,Fthe rate of the general population?
OL,11,FWhat help was given to our frontline
OL,12,Fstaff? Why were the psychiatric
OL,13,Fhospitals emptied at the same time
OL,14,Fthat community care was shut down?
OL,16,F"The inquiry was set up to examine the
OL,17,FUK's response to and impact of the
OL,18,FCovid-19 pandemic and learn lessons
OL,19,Ffor the future.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
