OL,3,CCovid-19 inquiry chairwoman accused of
OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,F"It cannot do this without an in-depth
OL,7,Fexamination of both the physical and
OL,8,Fmental health consequences of the
OL,9,Fpandemic. It must urgently reconsider
OL,10,Fits position."
OL,12,FRheian Davies, head of legal at Mind,
OL,13,Ftold PA the inquiry needs to "look at
OL,14,Fwhat happened to the nation's mental
OL,15,Fhealth and what political decisions `
OL,16,For mistakes ` were made that we
OL,17,Fwouldn't make again.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]uD@^OU
