OL,3,CCovid-19 inquiry chairwoman accused of
OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,F"For example, almost a quarter of the
OL,7,Fpsychiatric beds were emptied out and,
OL,8,Fat the same time, community services
OL,9,Fwere virtually shut down.
OL,11,F"So, people were released who wouldn't
OL,12,Fhave normally been discharged, or
OL,13,Fwould have been discharged with quite
OL,14,Fheavy community input.
OL,16,F"What they went into was nothing or
OL,17,Fnext to nothing...
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
