OL,3,CCovid-19 inquiry chairwoman accused of
OL,4,C'U-turn' over mental health impact
OL,6,F"Even people who rely on monthly
OL,7,Finjections of antipsychotics to stay
OL,8,Fwell were missing those injections,
OL,9,Fmissing that support.
OL,11,F"These are serious questions that the
OL,12,Finquiry should be grappling with.
OL,13,FWould we do that again? Is there
OL,14,Fanything to be learned from that?
OL,16,F"So, we've gone from what looks like a
OL,17,Fpromising situation back to nothing
OL,18,Fagain and she (Baroness Hallett) has
OL,19,Fsaid 'We don't have time', which we
OL,20,Factually don't agree with."
