OL,6,F"Public hearings for Module 3,
OL,7,Finvestigating the impact of the
OL,8,Fpandemic on the UK's healthcare
OL,9,Fsystems, will start in September 2024.
OL,10,FThey will include consideration of
OL,11,Finpatient Children and Adolescent
OL,12,FMental Health Services ` now referred
OL,13,Fto as Children and Young People's
OL,14,FMental Health Services. Other module
OL,15,Fhearings are scheduled to run until
