OL,6,FIt comes as the Centre for Mental
OL,7,FHealth said the mental health
OL,8,Fworkforce needs to keep growing over
OL,9,Fthe next decade to meet rising levels
OL,10,Fof demand.
OL,12,FChief executive Andy Bell said the
OL,13,Fworkforce also needs to diversify and
OL,14,Foffer people a wider range of
OL,15,Fopportunities to work in mental health.
